      • Portal

        public Portal​(Actor fromp,
              Actor top,
              boolean bidirectional,
              boolean wanderingp,
              boolean safep,
              boolean instantaneousp,
              java.lang.Long expiresatp,
              boolean invasionp)
        Parameters:
        fromp - Source town.
        top - Destination town.
        bidirectional - If true will allow travel back.
        wanderingp - If true the portal moves with time.
        safep - If false deals damage upon entering.
        instantaneousp - If false will take some time to get to the other side.
        expiresatp - See expiresat.
        invasionp - If true will periodically bring creatures from the other side until closed.
